2015-11-13 <grm@melexis.com>
    [*] \products\811xx\
    LIN Loader: Added Loader protection with the key for 811xx products [PLTF-734]

2015-11-09 <grm@melexis.com>
    [*] \products\813xx\
    Start-up updates:
        - Changed NVRAM CRC-routine from C-code to inline ASM (4x faster)
        - Changed TMTR-write into ASM too (20% faster) + Change copy routine to copy "blocks" of 4 words
    
2015-11-02 <grm@melexis.com>
    [*] \products\LIN-products\src\sys_mlx16.c
    The MLX16_RESET() has been updated to use digital WD as often as possible to produce device reset [PLTF-758]
    (see MLX82050-20 describing the problem with analog WD)
    
    The digital WD can be used for device reset if
        - Digital WD isn't enabled
        - DWD Window mode is enabled
        - DWD Intelligent mode is enabled
        - DWD Timer mode is enabled with Timeout < 1ms
    If DWD Timer mode is enabled with Timeout > 1ms, then analog WD with PLL disabling is used

2015-10-30 <grm@melexis.com>    
    [*] \products\LINLoader\config_ini\MLXLIN_default
    Configuration file was updated [PLTF-672]
        - TFastToLin=60000
        - TLinToFast=40000
        - TRestart=20000

2015-10-07 <grm@melexis.com>
    [*] \libsrc\LIN\flashupload.c
    Added conditional reset support for Loader [PLTF-750]

2015-10-01 <grm@melexis.com>
