2015-09-16 <grm@melexis.com>
    [*] \products\81106_7\(81108_9)
                  81150\
                  813xx\
                  LINLoader\
                  Validation\
    LIN API (MLX4 v4.1.0) support:
        - The lin2b_romtbl.S files were updated according to MLX4 v4.1.0 changes
        - The src\low_level_init.c files were updated as MLX4's RAM usage was desreased
        - ld-files were updated

2015-09-16 <grm@melexis.com>
    [*] \libsrc\LIN\
        \libsrc\Mlx4\
    LIN API: Updated MLX4 up to version 4.1.0
        - Frame mode is not more supported (removed ml_Transmit(), ml_Recieve(), mlu_HeaderRecieved())
        - Most of swithes for Mlx4 were disabled. The 'switches.asm' contains details
        - MLX4 private RAM reduced to 64 bytes
        - _IDInitTbl and _IDInitTbl2 tables were removed from LIN_CONFIG_TABLE
        - _AUTOADDtbl was moved to the end of LIN_CONFIG_TABLE
        - LIN_CONFIG_TABLE_ADDR can be aligned on 64-byte boundary (prev. 128-byte)
    LIN driver: Changes and optimisation as a part of update to MLX4 v4.1.0
        - Removed HAS_LIN_SET_OPTIONS as Mlx4 permanently supports ml_SetOptions()     
        - Removed HAS_LIN_GET_STATE option as since MLX4 v4.1 ml_GetState() permanently enabled
        - Removed HAS_LIN_DYNAMIC_ID option as MLX4 v4.1 permanently supports configurable IDs
    LIN driver rewiev:
        - Changed error ml_erCommand to ml_erShortDone
        - Renamed ml_WakeUpInit to ml_erWakeUpInit
        - Removed ml_erNextFrameIDCode error
        - Removed ml_FrameIDCode typedef
        - included ml_stSHORT into enumeration ml_LinState

2015-09-16 <grm@melexis.com>
    [*] \libsrc\LIN\flashfunctions_c_cmp.c
        \libsrc\LIN\flashupload.h
        \products\813xx\scr\premain.c
    LIN Loader: Added functionality to move Loader's page buffer on the stack.
                The 128 bytes into RAM are released
                The 'LDR_HAS_PAGE_BUFFER_ON_STACK' option was enabled for 813xx products      

2015-09-16 <grm@melexis.com>
