    Changed version number feature to support versions up to: 255.255.255.255

2013-09-10 <yso@melexis.com>
	[*] libsrc/MUPET
	Integrated new version of MUPET SW module 1.0.1:  
	- Implemented workaround for MLXCOMP-17 issue (volatile access optimization)
	  during accessing PTC_STS port
	- Added extra check that EEPROM write is done only in PTC mode (bit PTC_MODE,
      see issue MLX16107-148)

2013-09-10 <yso@melexis.com>
    [!] \libsrc\LIN\flashupload.c
    Fixed issue with incorrect behaviour when erase of more than one
    Flash page is requested.

2013-09-09 <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] lin.h
    lin_baudrate.h
    lincst.h 
    LIN driver include files are not copied to /include directory anymore to
    avoid duplications. Compiler searches for them directly in libsrc/LIN
    directory (directory is added to -I search in config\Config.mk)

2013-09-09 <yso@melexis.com>
    [!] \libsrc\sent\sent_cfg.c
    \libsrc\sent\sent_cfg.h
    Updated SENT component to version 0.1.1 (fixed bug PLTF-552)
    
2013-09-09 <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] bin/srec_cat.exe
    Updated srec_cat utility to version 1.60
    - There are now several additional CRC-16 polynomials, plus the ability
      to select a polynomial by name, rather than by value.

2013-09-09  <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] \config\Config.mk 
    Optiization option, e.g. -Os, is added also to assembler flags:
        OPTIMIZATION = -Os
        [...]
        ASFLAGS = $(OPTIMIZATION)

    This enables more optimization in mathlib functions implemented in assembly

    [*] \include\mathlib.h
    \libsrc\math
    Integrated new version of MLX16 mathlib (2.2.4)
       - Added DSP sub-component

	   - Optmized code size of divI32_I32byI16 function in case of co-processor
	     compilation.
	
       - Added mapping of MLX16 CPU variant to HAS_MLX16_COPROCESSOR
         and HAS_MLX16_FSB_SFB_INSTRUCTIONS defines which are further
         used by the mathlib instead of __MLX16_X8__ etc 

       - Form now on, conditional compilation in mathlib sources uses
         HAS_MLX16_COPROCESSOR and HAS_MLX16_FSB_SFB_INSTRUCTIONS instead of
        __MLX16_8__, __MLX16_X8__, __MLX16_FX__ etc to know which CPU instructions
        are available. 
     
       - Removed deprecated functions:  int8 divI8hi_I8byI8(int8 n, int8 d) and 
        int8 divI8hi_I8byU8(int8 n, uint8 d)

      - Changed overflow storage initialization from "SC <reg>" instruction
        to "MOV <reg>, #0" instruction to be compatible with MLX16-x8 and MLX16-FX
        (issue MLXSIM-53 and MLXCOMP-266)

      - Changed .include to #include in assembler files to be able to use -I <path>
        specified diring compilation

