             by calling  ml_SetDefaultBaudRate or ml_SetBaudRate function.

2013-01-24 <yso@melexis.com> release 3.0.14.0 ---------------------------------
2013-01-22 <yso@melexis.com>
	[+] \libsrc\Mlx4\lin2b_12mhz.bin
	\libsrc\Mlx4\lin2b_v13_9600_12mhz.bin
	\libsrc\Mlx4\lin2b_v13_19200_12mhz.bin
	\libsrc\Mlx4\lin2b_24mhz.bin
