    after write NVRAM command.

2012-11-15 <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] \libsrc\LIN\lin.h
    LIN: Specified shared RAM for MLX4/MLX16 as dp to speed up access for MLX16
    (on MULAN2 the shared memory is mapped into dp segment)

2012-11-12 <yso@melexis.com>
    [!] include\adclib.h
    ADC: Fixed ADC_TRIGGER_NEXT_CONVERSION() to clean interrupt flag _before_ starting
    an ADC conversion (issue PLTF-531)

2012-10-15 <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] MUPET library 
