    http://cvs.kiev.elex.be/cgi-bin/cvsweb/cvseseg/projects/feasibility/MUPeT_module

2012-10-10 <yso@melexis.com> release 3.0.12 ----------------------------------

2012-10-10 <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] flashfunctions_c_cmp.c
    flashfunctions_c.c
    LIN Loader: Removed extra cycle with writing 0xff to flash page before erase/write
    procedure (PLTF-526)

2012-10-10 <yso@melexis.com>
	[*] low_level_init.c
    Start-up: Changed low_level_init procedure for MULAN2
	- added initialization of TM_TR register for Flash trimming
	- added initialization of Flash extra wait-cycle (of needed)
	  and MLX16/MLX4 priority selection
    - 1MHz core timer calibration procedure changed: ANA_OUTC bit 15 is set to "1",
      independent of the NVRAM contents, and the CK_TRIM value is set to 64-PLL_Freq(MHz)   
	- added RAM test (executed on PLL clock)
		
    [*] products\81300\include\ioports.h 
    81300: Updated IO port description
    
2012-10-10 <yso@melexis.com>
    [+]lin2b.bin
    lin2b_v13_19200.bin
    lin2b_v13_9600.bin
