    lin2b_v13_19200_28mhz.bin
    lin2b_v13_9600_28mhz.bin 
    Added MLX4 LIN FW images for 28 MHz
	MLX4 LIN FW images is selected based on MCU_PLL_MULT (80 or 112) setting in the configuration
	profile: products\81300\config

