	Removed MLX4_LIN_FW_BIN. From now on, image file is selected by
	checking MLX4_FW_LIN2X, MLX4_FW_LIN13_9600, MLX4_FW_LIN13_19200
	or MLX4_FW_STANDALONE_LOADER define generated by Extra.mk 
	
2012-04-06 <yso@melexis.com>
