2011-09-23 <yso@melexis.com>
    [!] \libsrc\LIN\lin2b.bin
    Updated MLX4 LIN FW to version 3.1.5 (fixed bugs PLTF-476 and PLTF-477)
    	
2011-09-19 <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] nvram.h
    nvram.c
    Added NVRAM_SavePage function, removed NVRAM_Save

2011-09-18 <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] version.h
    Changed version numberin. For MULAN2/MMC16 from now on the
    __MLX_PLTF_VERSION_MAJOR__ will be 3. Currentl version is 3.0.1

    [*] nvram.h
    nvram.c
    Added function NVRAM_BufferFill to write bytes into NVRAM buffer

    [*] flashfunctions.h
    flashfunctions_c_cmp.c
    flashupload.c
    flashfunctions_c.c
    Changed Flash Driver API names: FlashRead to Flash_PageRead, FlashWrite
    to Flash_PageWrite, FlashDataWrite to Flash_PageBufferFill. Added
    Flash_PageErase.

    [+] flash_cfg.h
    flashfunctions_c_cmp.c
    Makefile
    [-] flashfunctions_wv.c
    Added Flash Driver which compare buffer with Flash Page after write/erase
    operation

    [+] flashfunctions_c.c
    [-] flashfunctions.c
    Makefile
    Added simple Flash driver w/o write/erase verification

    [*] flashupload_cfg.h
    flashupload.c
    Renamed LDR_HAS_FLASH_BLOCK_VERIFICATION to
    LDR_HAS_FLASH_WRITE_STATUS_REPORTING. Now this switch controls reporting
    of the write/erase status back to PC programming tool. Write/erase
    versification is configured separately by selecting appropriate
    Flash Driverin in libsrc/LIN/Makefile (e.g. flashfunctions_c_cmp.c)

    [*] flashupload.c
    1. Loader variables are moved to dp space.
    2. Optimized function ml_ReadData.
    3. Chip reports SW Platform Version instead of MLX4 LIN FW version in
       response to "Enter programming mode" frame (added ml_GetPlatformVersion)
    4. Optimized frame counter calculation for S2M CF frames.
    5. Renamed ml_TableAddress to _mlx_TableAddress and ml_TableSize to
       _mlx_TableSize for correct constant linking (constants should start
       with _mlx_ to be linked in first half of the flash)

    [*] flashupload.c
    1. Removed commands  ddExit, ddSlowProt (not used by programming tool anymore;
    command ddRestart is sent instead, see record MPT-111 on Jira)
    2. Added ddFlashPageErase command


2011-09-14  <atn@melexis.com>
    [*] flashupload.c
    Implemented EEPROM operations ddEeWrite and ddEeRead (controlled by
    LDR_HAS_EEPROM_COMMANDS switch)

    [*] flashupload.c
    lin.c
    lin.h
    ml_InitLinModule.c
    [+] lin_nad.h
    Added configuration of the loader's NAD (functions ml_SetLoaderNAD and
    ml_GetLoaderNAD)

    [*] Linker scripts
    Added ram_lin_fixed region/section

