    Revert back to version 2.6.50 due to PLTF-469 issue

2011-06-15 <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] config\Config.mk
    Removed "$(GCCDIR)/bin" prefix for binutils (sh, cp, rm etc)
    Starting from version 1.10 of mlx16-gcc the bunutils are moved to
    directory C:\mlx16-gcc\cygwin\bin, which must be is a system PATH.
    To summarize:
    Directories C:\mlx16-gcc\bin;C:\mlx16-gcc\cygwin\bin
    MUST be in a system PATH for correct building

2011-06-06 <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] Linker scripts
    Added NOLOAD type to .noinit section

