    [*] Config.mk 
    Added Trhex utility
2009-08-05   <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] Config.mk 
    Added compiler switch -mwith-itc-bug-workaround to fix [MULAN-5] issue

    [*] ioports.h
    mulan2_io.h
    Changed __SYS_ENTER_PROTECTED_MODE when preprocessor symbol
    __WITH_ITC_BUG_WORKAROUND__ is defined to fix [MULAN-5] issue

2009-07-20  <yso@melexis.com>
    [*] \include\syslib.h
    Added __always_inline__ to functions SYS_getCpuStatus, SYS_setCpuStatus and
    __statusCleanup to avoid function call with -O0 optimization level
    Added function SYS_clearCpuStatus to clear M register (SYS_setCpuStatus(0)
    created local variable with -O0 which is not acceptable)

2009-02-13  <yso@melexis.com>
    Initial outline

    
